{"tid":2104942,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人熄電腦會熄埋火牛?","createTime":"2020-07-12T09:59:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-12T11:21:57.000Z","uid":335003,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"60a04451ad8dbb0b4335449b97bf3e12d7daf0ef","tid":2104942,"uid":335003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T09:59:56.000Z","msg":"主要係由於而字好多 mouse 之類配件都會在熄咗電腦後長期著燈。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果好似我咁電腦放睡房嘅，真係俾呢啲 週邊配件s 殘眼到瞓唔到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以我特登擺到部主機位方便熄埋火牛掣， 熄完電腦過一排就直接熄埋隻牛，等啲配件唔著燈。<br />\n<br />\n最多咪底板電池換密多少少咁多囉。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n設計啲備用燈在電腦熄完都仲著嘅廠商，尤其果啲所謂備用燈五光十色&amp;光到好似RGB 正常運作嘅樣但又唔係個產品盒寫明嘅契弟們<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">我屌曬你哋老母</span></span>"},{"pid":"de6220fd4f1af79b20ec77f9e869ba9872f43cce","tid":2104942,"uid":63,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T10:00:57.000Z","msg":"底板有得set 閂機唔供電比usb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1f15c680283c255d724b24640e5643869107cbb","tid":2104942,"uid":54177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T10:03:29.000Z","msg":"bios好似有得set<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"633f4a29a36efd76c47953370dc5cf89c6a7533e","tid":2104942,"uid":140726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T10:15:34.000Z","msg":"熄埋屋企大掣"},{"pid":"24d18df4cf6a38272df88d47e3c62436d78a25e1","tid":2104942,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T10:16:25.000Z","msg":"唔識喺BIOS熄？"},{"pid":"497b3b96bde05612917e24baf5c3ea9505fd22ae